3. cs.LG (Machine Learning) - The paper involves the use of deep learning models and optimization techniques, which are core topics in cs.LG. 
4. cs.IR (Information Retrieval) - The task of semantic parsing involves retrieving relevant information from a given text, which is a key aspect of information retrieval. 
5. cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) - The use of neural networks in the proposed system makes it relevant to cs.NE.
